'''费莉莎·沃尔夫－西蒙'''（{{lang-en|Felisa Wolfe-Simon}}）是一位美国[[微生物学|微生物]][[地球生物学|地球生物学]]和[[生物地球化学|生物地球化学]]家。

==生平==
2010年，沃尔夫－西蒙领导的团队发现了一种[[嗜極生物|嗜極细菌]][[GFAJ-1|GFAJ-1]]，可在高含[[砷|砷]]低含[[磷|磷]]的条件下生长<ref name="Wolfe-Simon et al 2010">{{cite journal|last1=Wolfe-Simon|first1=F.|last2=Blum|first2=J. S.|last3=Kulp|first3=T. R.|last4=Gordon|first4=G. W.|last5=Hoeft|first5=S. E.|last6=Pett-Ridge|first6=J.|last7=Stolz|first7=J. F.|last8=Webb|first8=S. M.|last9=Weber|first9=P. K.|last10=Davies|first10=P. C. W.|last11=Anbar|first11=A. D.|last12=Oremland|first12=R. S.|title=A Bacterium That Can Grow by Using Arsenic Instead of Phosphorus|journal=Science|date=2010|volume=332|issue=6034|pages=1163–1166|doi=10.1126/science.1197258|pmid=21127214|bibcode = 2011Sci...332.1163W |doi-access=free}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Wolfe-Simon|first1=F.|last2=Blum|first2=J. S.|last3=Kulp|first3=T. R.|last4=Gordon|first4=G. W.|last5=Hoeft|first5=S. E.|last6=Pett-Ridge|first6=J.|last7=Stolz|first7=J. F.|last8=Webb|first8=S. M.|last9=Weber|first9=P. K.|last10=Davies|first10=P. C. W.|last11=Anbar|first11=A. D.|last12=Oremland|first12=R. S.|title=Response to Comments on "A Bacterium That Can Grow Using Arsenic Instead of Phosphorus"|journal=Science|date=27 May 2011|volume=332|issue=6034|pages=1149|doi=10.1126/science.1202098|bibcode = 2011Sci...332.1149W |doi-access=free}}</ref>，最初沃尔夫－西蒙认为这种细菌可能使用[[砷酸|砷酸]]替代[[磷酸|磷酸]]作为[[DNA|DNA]]的骨架<ref>Drahl, C. The Arsenic-Based-Life Aftermath. Researchers challenge a sensational claim, while others revisit arsenic biochemistry, Chem Eng News 90(5), 42-47, January 30, 2012. http://cen.acs.org/articles/90/i5/Arsenic-Based-Life-Aftermath.html {{Wayback|url=http://cen.acs.org/articles/90/i5/Arsenic-Based-Life-Aftermath.html |date=20160303181539 }}; accessed 13 October 2012</ref>，但后来[[罗茜·雷德菲尔德|罗茜·雷德菲尔德]]等人的实验证明这种细菌只是抵抗砷而非利用砷<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Erb|first1=T. J.|last2=Kiefer|first2=P.|last3=Hattendorf|first3=B.|last4=Gunther|first4=D.|last5=Vorholt|first5=J. A.|title=GFAJ-1 Is an Arsenate-Resistant, Phosphate-Dependent Organism|journal=Science|date=2012|volume=337|issue=6093|pages=467–470|doi=10.1126/science.1218455|bibcode = 2012Sci...337..467E|pmid=22773139}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Reaves|first1=M. L.|last2=Sinha|first2=S.|last3=Rabinowitz|first3=J. D.|last4=Kruglyak|first4=L.|last5=Redfield|first5=R. J.|title=Absence of Detectable Arsenate in DNA from Arsenate-Grown GFAJ-1 Cells|journal=Science|date=2012|volume=337|issue=6093|pages=470–473|doi=10.1126/science.1219861|arxiv = 1201.6643 |bibcode = 2012Sci...337..470R|pmid=22773140|pmc=3845625}}</ref>。

